ResourceHeader.ResourceName: Ulysses Heliosphere Instrument for Spectral, Composition, and Anisotropy at Low Energies (HISCALE) LEMS120 MFSA, Solar Wind Frame, Sectored Proton Fluxes, Daily Averages
ResourceHeader.Description: Daily-averaged sectored proton fluxes from the MF Spectrum Analyzer of the Ulysses/HISCALE LEMS120 instrument. All energies thresholds take into account the incident particle type, shielding, and inactive dead-layer of the solid state detector. All fluxes are background corrected and are in the solar wind rest frame.
ResourceHeader.Acknowledgement: Thomas P. Armstrong, Fundamental Technologies, LLC
